==English==

===Etymology===
From [[w:Robert Boyle|Robert Boyle]] Irish natural philosopher

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Boyle]]’s [[law]]'''
#{{physics}} the observation that the [[pressure]] of an [[ideal gas]] is [[inversely proportional]] to its [[volume]] at constant [[temperature]]

